        <p> <p><a name="weapons">Forged Weapons (NEW):<p>It is now possible to use your
            blacksmithing skill to create weapons!  These new weapons are
            called, "Forged Weapons."  They are non-magical, but
            are rather good weapons for lower levels.  <p>The weapons
            are made exactly the same way as you make armor.  Simply place
            the components into the forge and hit combine.  Making weapons
            its one of the more profitable parts of blacksmithing.  These
            weapons are pretty good, and can sell for a lot to lower
            levels.  <p>Here is a list of some known confirmed
            recipes:<p> 
